@startuml
!theme cerulean
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam shadowing false
title Amazon Marketplace Analytics - Control Flow (Query Decision State)

[*] --> ReceiveQuery
ReceiveQuery --> ValidateIdentity
ValidateIdentity --> Reject : invalid token / tenant
ValidateIdentity --> ParseIntent : valid user

ParseIntent --> KPIRequest : summary / metric request
ParseIntent --> TrendRequest : time-series request
ParseIntent --> ComparisonRequest : compare products / regions
ParseIntent --> DiagnosticRequest : ambiguous or follow-up analysis

KPIRequest --> QueryAnalyticsDB
TrendRequest --> QueryAnalyticsDB
ComparisonRequest --> QueryAnalyticsDB
DiagnosticRequest --> UseAgentTooling

UseAgentTooling --> QueryAnalyticsDB
QueryAnalyticsDB --> SelectVisualization

SelectVisualization --> RenderLineChart : trend
SelectVisualization --> RenderBarChart : comparison
SelectVisualization --> RenderPieChart : distribution
SelectVisualization --> RenderTable : detailed drill-down

RenderLineChart --> [*]
RenderBarChart --> [*]
RenderPieChart --> [*]
RenderTable --> [*]
Reject --> [*]
@enduml
